=== How to use ===

== Compiling ==

The project is built using Maven2. Please install Maven2 and run

$ mvn compile

All dependencies will be downloaded automatically.

== Running ==

$ ./run.sh [options]

or (in source/ directory)

$ mvn exec:java

== Hacking with Eclipse ==

To integrate the project in eclipse, one has two options:

1. Install the marvelous m2e eclipse plugin, go to File->New->Import
   and select "Existing maven project..."

2. Run
$ mvn eclipse:eclipse
   to generate .project and .classpath files and load the project as 
   you would load a normal eclipse project.

== Packaging ==

The following command will produce the release tarball in target/polygonsSWP-release.tar.gz.

$ mvn package

